title: Person of Interest - 2x19 'Trojan Horse' - Walk in the dark
author: POISuit
comment: Ever since the series ended I watched it at least twice every year. This show is exceptional and those clips really show it. I just love how this show built all this characters, connected them and everything else basically.

Merry Christmas! I sometimes wonder if POI was as good as I remember... and then you post a clip reminding me why I loved it so much. It has so much heart. These amazing heart wrenching moments that resonate.
A friend once told me "in our line of work, we walk in the dark." Doesn't mean we have to walk in it alone.
Wow, what was the reason you started uploading again? That's so cool! Welcome back!
